# Rust build artifacts
crate/target/
target/

# Node
node_modules/

# OS
.DS_Store

# NOTE: pkg/ (prebuilt WASM + JS glue) IS committed so the CLI runs without a
# Rust toolchain. Rebuild with `npm run build:wasm`.
#
# Likewise docs/pkg/ (web-target WASM) IS committed so GitHub Pages can serve
# the browser playground statically. Rebuild with `npm run build:web`.
#
# pkg-web/ (web-target WASM shipped in the npm tarball for the browser build)
# IS committed too. `npm run build:web` regenerates pkg-web/ and copies it into
# docs/pkg/.
